### Students API

### Get all students
GET http://localhost:3000/students

### Get student by ID
# @name getStudent
GET http://localhost:3000/students/1

### Create a new student
# This will create a student named "Jane Doe" and link them to the course with ID 1.
POST http://localhost:3000/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Doe",
  "promotion": "Spring-2026",
  "courses": [1]
}

### Update a student
PATCH http://localhost:3000/students/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe Updated"
}

### Delete a student
DELETE http://localhost:3000/students/2


### Courses API

### Get all courses
GET http://localhost:3000/courses

### Get course by ID
# @name getCourse
GET http://localhost:3000/courses/1

### Create a new course
POST http://localhost:3000/courses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Advanced TypeScript",
  "description": "A deep dive into advanced TypeScript features."
}

### Update a course
PATCH http://localhost:3000/courses/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "An updated and more detailed course description."
}

### Delete a course
DELETE http://localhost:3000/courses/2


### Linking Courses to Students

### Add a course to a student
# This will add the course with ID 2 to the student with ID 1.
POST http://localhost:3000/students/1/courses/2

